                        <p class="welcome">Welcome to ADAM</p>
						<p class="adam_wel">A web-based tool which gathers information from diverse databases to help users to:</p>
					   <ul class="top-container-list">
							 <li>Identify sources of funding for agriculture-related activities.</li>
							 <li>Determine FAO comparative advantages.</li>
							 <li>Formulate resource mobilization strategies.</li>
