						<p class="indent" id="adam-label"> <img src="adam-images/adam_view.gif" title="Click to open the ADAM View"  /><br/></p>
						<p class="minitext"> Find out which resource partners are operating where and when. Match their activities to the priorities of a country/region and assess FAO's comparative advantage using FAO's Strategic Framework or the DAC sector classification. </p>
					    <p align="center"><img src="adam-images/adam-view.png" width="230px" alt="" /></p>
					    <p class="gototext" id="adam-go"> Go to ADAM View <img src="adam-images/more.png"></p>
					</div>
					<div id="column2">
						<p class="indent" id="matrix-label"><img src="adam-images/matrix.gif" title="Click to open the Resource Partner Matrix" /><br/></p>
						<p class="minitext"> Create a detailed snapshot of resource partners' recent/past activity and rank most likely resource partners. View partner commitments as total Official Development Assistance (ODA) as well as by agricultural related subsectors.</p>
						<p align="center"><img src="adam-images/matrix-view.png" width="230px" alt="" /></p>
						<p class="gototext" id="matrix-go"> Go to Resource Partner Matrix <img src="adam-images/more.png"></p>
					</div>
					<div id="column3">
						<p class="indent" id="profile-label"><img src="adam-images/profile.gif" title="Click to open the Resource Partner Profiles" /><br/></p>
						<p class="minitext">Gather information on a resource partner's stated priority themes matched with FAO's Strategic Framework, spending patterns, favoured funding mechanisms and internal processes. Contacts and web links are also provided. </p>
                        <p class="colimage"><img src="adam-images/profile-view.png" width="230px" border="0" alt="" /></p>
                        <p class="gototext" id="profile-go"> Go to Resource Partner Profiles <img src="adam-images/more.png"></p>
